Package shopping_webcrawler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ResultObject
    ResultObject is the item listed on the web page ResultObject describes the details about the item
    ResultPage
    ResultPage is the page information generated from parsed document return by WebCrawler ResultPage can parse the information of each item
    WebCrawler
    WebCrawler crawls web page information from specific website This WebCrawler is focused on "http://www.shopping.com"
